{
  "texts": [
    "Data Integrity.",
    "We conducted comprehensive validation to ensure that all datasets used in FLAME were of acceptable quality for use.",
    "Before including a dataset, we conduct manual or semiautomated checks for label mismatch, duplicate entries, and incomplete annotations.",
    "If the dataset is well-documented and widely cited as reliable, we fast-track its inclusion.",
    "Community Collaboration."
  ]
}